{"tid":199984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"year1 engine仔揀科 要考慮啲咩因素","createTime":"2017-04-13T15:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:19:01.000Z","uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2b9371de22c05b18b0a03d7967fea722cda164","tid":199984,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"小弟讀緊UST year1 Engine<br />\n仲有2個月就左右就要揀major<br />\n我都知自己問得遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同屋企人都係睇錢途，而且我好想留係香港工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住出黎有穩定收入嘅工作就得<br />\n咁我係咪揀土木工程就最穩陣？<br />\n但係我聽人講就快冇晒十大基建，所以會難請人......<br />\n我睇返上年起薪點又真係好似少咗，唔知係咪我錯覺呢......<br />\n而又有人話土木工程唔會飽和，因為污水等等嘅項目都有份佢哋做，至少請到人<br />\n<br />\n除咗土木工程，半年前我仲心郁郁，考慮過航空工程（要入咗機電先再讀到航空，都係讀4年）<br />\n聽人講UST教嘅航空工程，唔係關於本地，而係關於外國野<br />\n啫係本地搵工冇咩幫助..？定係啲老闆望到張cert就會加分，考慮請我？<br />\n聽啲師兄講，最弊嘅係讀機電嘅可以做航空，但係讀航空嘅唔可以做機電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽落去，讀完航空好似未必幫到我係本地到搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係，如果真係去到機場做，晉升機會係咪點都多過土木工程？<br />\n<br />\n我又問過啲親戚，佢哋話揀major要睇得長遠啲，即使頭幾年人工低，但係日後升到職又加人工，其實好過打一份人工升得慢嘅工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦，我講咁多，其實都係想搵份穩定啲嘅工，想各位巴打認為我讀土木定機電好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果各位巴打覺得我一開始個方向已經錯咗，直接屌我就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0119ee15a648f1dbd911b0aef3a90b829eacd2c","tid":199984,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"ust機電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562bec8104c657c9365edb894a5e561512b636ce","tid":199984,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"Mech grad表示讀咩都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305d13f52329aa5329a3558f25936086d8b60bfe","tid":199984,"uid":78166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"ust有機電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw mech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7160c4206bd21f1f3f5ca3a369704681eadbad94","tid":199984,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"機電做到航天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7d3d7a837868eec12a630814edd1a6140eaab7","tid":199984,"uid":28250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"讀航天要係mech 簡wo<br />\n唔係機電<br />\nbtw 若要生活好<br />\n咪撚讀Civil"},{"pid":"85abcd773e5f075b12ee2dddb0a52eb8ab0459c9","tid":199984,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠<br />\n因為我都講開mech 即係機械<br />\n點知打返中文就變成機電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0df96f6fb70cd0ef145edbd17f01a7d08b493b","tid":199984,"uid":104952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T01:16:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dda6bbb3b5e5db8f12e565adc6ce67cde795f3b","tid":199984,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"civil比人逼爆左未"},{"pid":"7f25b080577f4f651078a24bd1f818af7c7dc95d","tid":199984,"uid":183117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主on 9仔來"}]}